**Title**: Route Survey Payload Deep Water Tender Notice
 **Reference Number**: cb-7922-13764678
 **Solicitation Number**: W8482-241708/A

**Publication Date**: August 9, 2023
 **Tender Closing Date**: September 8, 2023, at 14:00:00 ECT

**Tender Status**: Expired

**UNSPSC**: 41115200 Radar and sonar systems and components

**Procurement Category**: Goods and Defence (GD)
 **Notice Type**: Request for Proposal

**Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open bidding
 **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price

**Trade Agreements**: Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

**Regions of Opportunity**: Canada
**Regions of Delivery**: British Columbia, Nova Scotia

**Contracting Entity**: National Defence
**Contracting Entity Address**: 101 Colonel By Drive, Ottawa, ON K1A 0K2

**Contact Information**:

* Name: Ashley Nadeau-Weeks
* Email: Ashley.Nadeau-Weeks@forces.gc.ca
* Phone: (555) 555-5555

**Notice URL**: None
 **Attachment**:
  • English RFP clauses: https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/7922/english-rfp-clauses_0.pdf
  • French RFP clauses: https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/7922/french-rfp-clauses.pdf

**Tender Description**: The Department of National Defence invites proposals for the supply of radar and sonar systems and components as outlined below. Delivery is requested to Canadian Forces Base (CFB) Halifax, Nova Scotia, and CFB Esquimalt, British Columbia.

* Item 1: Sounding Set, Sonar (GSIN: N5845, NSN: 01-5375226, FIN), Part No.: 14202028, NCAGE: 52315, Klein Marine Systems
* Item 2: Sounding Set, Sonar (GSIN: N5845, NSN: 01-5375226, FIN), Part No.: 14202028, NCAGE: 52315, Klein Marine Systems
* Item 3: Accessory Kit (GSIN: N5845, NSN: 20-A0R3181, FIN), Part No.: 141
